---
import astroLogo from "../assets/astro.svg";
import background from "../assets/background.svg";
import Card from "./Card.astro";
---

<div class="font-sans">
  <nav class="bg-black/90 backdrop-blur-sm border-b border-white/10">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 flex justify-between items-center h-14">
      <a href="/" class="font-bold text-white">TaskRatchet</a>
      <a href="/login" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white">Login</a>
    </div>
  </nav>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-6">
    <img
      class="fixed inset-0 w-full -z-10 blur-[100px]"
      src={background.src}
      alt=""
      fetchpriority="high"
    />
    <main class="flex justify-center">
      <section class="flex flex-col justify-center p-4">
        <h1
          class="text-5xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-[#3245ff] to-[#bc52ee] bg-clip-text text-transparent"
        >
          Put Money on Your Goals
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl max-w-2xl text-gray-200 leading-normal py-6">
          Ready to finally get things done? TaskRatchet helps you stay
          accountable by putting a friendly price tag on procrastination. Set
          your own deadlines, choose your stakes, and watch your productivity
          soar.
        </p>
        <section class="flex gap-4">
          <a
            class="text-white px-3 py-2.5 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-r from-[#3245ff] to-[#bc52ee] shadow-[inset_0_0_0_1px_rgba(255,255,255,0.12),inset_0_-2px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.24)] hover:shadow-none transition-shadow"
            href="#signup">Try It Free</a
          >
          <a
            class="text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-200 flex items-center px-3 py-2.5 no-underline transition-colors"
            href="#how-it-works">How It Works</a
          >
        </section>
      </section>
    </main>
    <div class="space-y-12 mt-12">
      <Card id="features">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">How It Works</h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed text-gray-300">
          1. Tell us what you want to accomplish<br />
          2. Choose how much to stake (it's up to you!)<br />
          3. Get it done and keep your money ðŸŽ‰
        </p>
      </Card>

      <Card id="accountability">
        <h2>Real Accountability</h2>
        <p>
          We're not just another todo list - we're your accountability partner.
          By putting a bit of money on the line, you're making a promise to your
          future self that you intend to keep.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4">
          Completed the task but forgot to check it off? No worries! Just reply
          to the charge notification and we'll cancel the charge for you.
        </p>
      </Card>

      <Card id="integrations">
        <h2>Integrations</h2>
        <p>Seamlessly connects with Beeminder to track your goals.</p>
      </Card>

      <Card id="team">
        <h2>Our Team</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6 mt-4">
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-medium mb-2">Nathan Arthur - Founder</h3>
            <p>
              Built TaskRatchet to make it easier to make monetary commitments
              on one-off tasks. Active in the Beeminder community since 2018.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-medium mb-2">Nicky - Customer Support</h3>
            <p>
              Keeps the inbox squeaky-clean and has improved customer support by
              several orders of magnitude since late 2022.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-medium mb-2">Luke Arthur - Developer</h3>
            <p>
              Joined to create TaskRatchet's mobile apps. Brings an engineering
              mindset and love of learning to push TaskRatchet forward.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </Card>

      <Card>
        <h2>Gain calmness and clarity with real accountability</h2>
        <a
          class="text-white px-3 py-2.5 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-r from-[#3245ff] to-[#bc52ee] shadow-[inset_0_0_0_1px_rgba(255,255,255,0.12),inset_0_-2px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.24)] hover:shadow-none transition-shadow inline-block mt-4"
          href="#signup">Try It Free</a
        >
      </Card>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
